17
00:02:19,306 --> 00:02:23,048
We must respect
all living creatures,

18
00:02:25,129 --> 00:02:27,333
except for the police,

19
00:02:27,369 --> 00:02:29,508
people who work
in government,

20
00:02:29,545 --> 00:02:31,269
bankers,
usurers,

21
00:02:33,674 --> 00:02:36,456
and anyone who has
the power and money

22
00:02:36,489 --> 00:02:39,075
to exploit
simple people.

23
00:02:39,114 --> 00:02:42,562
Stealing from this people
is allowed.

24
00:02:43,817 --> 00:02:48,325
But remember:
It's crazy to want too much.

25
00:02:53,226 --> 00:02:55,915
Men cannot possess more

26
