57
00:06:22,163 --> 00:06:24,881
And what are you doing wandering around here
all by yourself, anyway?

58
00:06:24,979 --> 00:06:28,394
I'm lost.
I forgot everything.

59
00:06:29,907 --> 00:06:31,151
I better go home.

60
00:06:33,011 --> 00:06:35,401
- You sure you're okay?
- Yes, sir.

61
