- Silence! Listen, you piece of shit!
- Kolyma!

83
00:09:00,634 --> 00:09:04,628
Take your hands off
my grandfather, you pig!

84
00:09:14,426 --> 00:09:16,467
Comrade Commander,
The place is full of...

85
00:09:24,379 --> 00:09:26,768
