has been hurt.

88
00:09:34,139 --> 00:09:39,027
Do you realize what times we live in,
brother Plank?

89
00:09:39,323 --> 00:09:43,546
Not even in our homes
can we find peace.

90
00:09:43,771 --> 00:09:47,164
True, but we are always
with you, Grandpa Kuzya,

91
00:09:47,164 --> 00:09:49,401
