broke three rules.

105
00:10:44,926 --> 00:10:47,359
He took a weapon without
the permission of an adult

106
00:10:47,359 --> 00:10:49,150
He took it from the red corner,

107
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:51,967
and he attempted to
fire it inside the house.

108
00:10:51,967 --> 00:10:54,782
These are things one
should never do!

109
00:10:54,815 --> 00:10:56,059
Never!

110
00:10:58,687 --> 00:11:01,370
