You must find who did it.

763
01:22:02,897 --> 01:22:04,652
Mel will go with you.

764
01:22:05,489 --> 01:22:08,272
I loaded this
with my own hands.

765
01:22:08,817 --> 01:22:10,956
That means you have
the right to use it

766
01:22:10,993 --> 01:22:13,514
to kill whoever
must be killed.

767
01:22:13,937 --> 01:22:16,589
This is the task
reserved for you.

768
01:22:17,938 --> 01:22:19,018
Why me?

769
01:22:19,986 --> 01:22:22,474
Be careful how you answer,
Grandfather Kuzya.

770
01:22:22,674 --> 01:22:25,063
There is no turning back once
you kill someone.

771
01:22:48,243 --> 01:22:50,218
Go! Go!

772
01:22:50,323 --> 01:22:51,371
Go!

773
01:22:51,666 --> 01:22:53,805
Go!

774
01:22:53,907 --> 01:22:55,631
Get out!

775
01:23:00,980 --> 01:23:02,801
Come on!

776
01:23:13,973 --> 01:23:15,565
Grandfather!

777
01:23:27,541 --> 01:23:32,210
The Mongols call Siberia,
"The Sleeping Land."

778
01:23:33,205 --> 01:23:36,947
I want to go back there
and lay down.

779
01:23:58,518 --> 01:24:00,787
Ok, we've got a car

780
01:24:00,918 --> 01:24:02,707
guns and enough money to
loosen some tongues.

781
01:24:03,254 --> 01:24:04,886
All of the clans have been notified

782
01:24:04,886 --> 01:24:06,196
and they're willing
to collaborate.

783
01:24:06,454 --> 01:24:10,732
So, hunting season
begins tonight, Mel.

784
01:24:11,958 --> 01:24:14,325
I'd like to bring my mother a fish.

785
01:24:15,094 --> 01:24:17,364
She really loves fish.

786
01:24:21,111 --> 01:24:23,598
I haven't gone fishing
in so long.

787
01:24:24,566 --> 01:24:27,829
Since we lost Vitalic.

788
01:24:31,479 --> 01:24:33,072
Kolyma!

789
01:24:34,360 --> 01:24:37,174
I heard you, Mel, but
now's not the time, okay?

790
01:24:37,463 --> 01:24:40,693
I dont' feel like it and besides,
we don't have any equipment.

791
01:24:40,887 --> 01:24:42,262
If that's the reason,

792
01:24:42,296 --> 01:24:44,467
you will find everything you need
in the toolshed.

793
01:24:49,336 --> 01:24:52,401
Nobody has set foot in here
since Gagarin has left.

794
01:24:52,728 --> 01:24:54,189
You will need a flashlight.

795
01:25:28,634 --> 01:25:31,416
Finally! Yes! The rod!

796
01:25:31,898 --> 01:25:34,964
And the drill should be here somewhere.
Help me.

797
01:26:52,605 --> 01:26:55,191
Is that where you left your switchblade?

798
01:26:56,702 --> 01:26:58,840
Kolyma!

799
01:27:03,165 --> 01:27:07,541
And the switchblade placed
in the door of a house...

800
01:27:07,581 --> 01:27:12,055
means that a meeting of
destinies will take place there.

801
01:27:49,183 --> 01:27:51,322
You sure took your time finding me!

802
01:27:52,032 --> 01:27:55,448
Any longer, you and I, we'll
have to die of old age.

803
01:27:56,928 --> 01:27:58,554
It wasn't easy.

804
01:27:58,848 --> 01:28:02,623
I never thought I'd
see you wearing that.

805
01:28:03,936 --> 01:28:05,213
It's horrible.

806
01:28:07,649 --> 01:28:09,209
It is horrible...

807
01:28:09,857 --> 01:28:12,223
but enlisting was
the only way to find you.

808
01:28:39,393 --> 01:28:42,296
Oh, I forgot you don't drink.

809
01:28:44,290 --> 01:28:46,656
The Russians are right on your tail,
Gagarin.

810
01:28:46,881 --> 01:28:48,770
Lots of them.

811
01:28:49,218 --> 01:28:51,422
You won't even know you're dead.

812
01:28:52,963 --> 01:28:54,850
And this isn't good, right?

813
01:28:55,330 --> 01:28:57,752
Because you want to be the one
to kill me.

814
01:29:01,795 --> 01:29:03,420
Strange.

815
01:29:03,619 --> 01:29:07,231
After all this time,
whenever I think about you,

816
01:29:07,331 --> 01:29:09,697
I still picture you as a boy.

817
01:29:28,547 --> 01:29:30,370
Xenya's ribbon.

818
01:29:30,467 --> 01:29:33,053
I found it in Aunt Katya's toolshed.

819
01:29:33,476 --> 01:29:36,640
It's stained with her blood;
so was the wall

820
01:29:37,668 --> 01:29:39,839
and the mattress where you slept.

821
01:29:49,381 --> 01:29:51,235
I'm listening.

822
01:29:52,132 --> 01:29:53,595
You want the whole story?

823
01:29:53,701 --> 01:29:56,122
It's not like those ones
your grandfather used to tell!

824
01:29:56,165 --> 01:29:58,532
- There is no moral here.
- Just tell me why.

825
01:29:58,628 --> 01:30:01,858
There is no why. No reason.
And no excuses either!

826
01:30:02,533 --> 01:30:05,566
It just happened.
Sucks, doesn't it?

827
01:30:10,309 --> 01:30:12,611
I destroy everything I touch.

828
01:30:19,974 --> 01:30:22,495
Grandfather loaded it for me.

829
01:30:29,510 --> 01:30:31,397
I've been waiting for you.

830
01:30:33,222 --> 01:30:35,335
I kept looking towards the woods, every day,

831
01:30:35,335 --> 01:30:38,117
trying to imagine when exactly you'd appear.

832
01:30:39,718 --> 01:30:41,791
I missed you, you know?

833
01:30:41,991 --> 01:30:43,998
We've had great company.

834
01:30:45,800 --> 01:30:49,728
I was always alone, Kolyma.
I've been alone my whole life!

835
01:30:50,695 --> 01:30:53,095
When I got out of jail,
I said to myself:

836
01:30:53,095 --> 01:30:55,364
"You belong to no one
and no one belongs to you!

837
01:30:55,495 --> 01:30:57,634
"And since the game is dirty,
No rules!

838
01:30:57,735 --> 01:31:00,997
"Take everything you can without asking.
Without saying 'thank you!'

839
01:31:01,063 --> 01:31:04,608
"Because no one, no one is going to
give you anything. Not for free! "

840
01:31:07,304 --> 01:31:11,679
But instead, I ended
up in this shithole.

841
01:31:19,240 --> 01:31:22,088
I want to go back, Kolyma.

842
01:31:26,601 --> 01:31:28,772
There is only one way.

843
01:31:32,937 --> 01:31:35,109
I know.

844
01:32:23,371 --> 01:32:25,990
And when a criminal
dies,

845
01:32:26,058 --> 01:32:29,736
his switchblade
must be broken.

846
01:32:29,802 --> 01:32:32,520
One part remains
with him,

847
01:32:33,323 --> 01:32:39,041
The other part, with the person whom
he loves most in this world.

848
01:32:39,180 --> 01:32:40,522
Why?

849
01:32:40,812 --> 01:32:43,811
Because that way
on Judgment Day,

850
01:32:43,885 --> 01:32:46,786
They can find
each other

851
01:32:46,860 --> 01:32:50,373
And be reunited in peace.

852
01:33:22,157 --> 01:33:24,328
Dear mama,
you were right...

853
01:33:24,910 --> 01:33:27,430
Some choices don't allow you
to turn back.

854
01:33:27,534 --> 01:33:29,956
And now, I can never
come home again.

855
01:33:30,701 --> 01:33:34,084
I think of you often.
Take care of yourself.

856
01:33:35,118 --> 01:33:38,217
I've decided to follow the sun
and will go west.

857
01:33:38,959 --> 01:33:40,846
I'm not sure what
my future holds,

858
01:33:40,846 --> 01:33:44,195
but I can tattoo,
use a knife and shoot a gun.

859
01:33:44,655 --> 01:33:46,312
Don't worry about me.

860
01:33:46,606 --> 01:33:49,127
I will stop you must fight life

861
01:33:49,326 --> 01:33:51,562
and I'll know how to.

